@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Task Manager";
    ViewBag.Message = "Efficiently Manage Your Tasks";
}

<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
    <h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <p>Welcome to Task Manager, your go-to platform for organizing and managing your tasks effectively. Our mission is to simplify your workflow and boost productivity by providing a user-friendly task management solution.</p>

    <p>Whether you are an individual looking to stay organized or a team collaborating on projects, Task Manager offers the tools you need to streamline your tasks, set deadlines, and track progress.</p>

    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Intuitive task creation and management</li>
        <li>Clear visibility into due dates and completion status</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Get started today and experience the efficiency of Task Manager in helping you achieve your goals and meet deadlines.</p>
</main>
